'''Fiber''' is a [[:Category:Resources|resource]] obtained by destroying [[Weeds]] or harvesting fully-grown [[Fiber Seeds]]. Each weed has a 50% chance to drop 1 Fiber when cut with a [[Scythe]], [[Axes|Axe]], [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]], [[Hoes|Hoe]], or [[Weapons#Sword|Sword]], or blown up by a [[Crafting#Bombs|bomb]]. The [[Desert Trader]] will also exchange five [[stone]] for one fiber on [[Days of the Week#Tuesday|Tuesdays]].

Weeds that drop Fiber can frequently be found in high quantities on Floors 25-29 and 81-109 of [[the Mines]]. The late-game [[Mutant Bug Lair]] is also a good source, generating 40-70 fiber from its weeds, which regenerate every few days.

[[Wilderness Golem]]s on the [[Farm Maps|Wilderness Farm map]] have a 90% chance of dropping Fiber, and a 50% chance of dropping a second Fiber, when slain.

Fiber is always normal quality.

