==Tailoring==
Fiber is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable [[Tailoring|Basic Pullover]].
*Male version: [[File:Shirt176.png|24px]]
*Female version: [[File:Shirt177.png|24px]]
It is a green dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the green dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
15 Fiber may be requested by [[Crayfish]], [[Periwinkle]], or [[Snail]] in a [[Fish Pond#Quests|Fish Pond quest]] to increase the capacity of the pond from 3 to 5..

